    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/1b0ddb8e06b216bdc172623ecc27629d.avif?t=1757359519\" width=630 height=73 /></span><br><br>Design your home and your shop exactly to your liking. Place furniture, decorate walls and ceilings,<br>or simply change the wallpaper and flooring. <br>Create a unique atmosphere that delights both you and your customers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/93111114ae73ef163c17b65f82a168a3.poster.avif?t=1757359519\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/93111114ae73ef163c17b65f82a168a3.webm?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/93111114ae73ef163c17b65f82a168a3.mp4?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/e355b6dff7bb9021565d74ee96ff17ab.avif?t=1757359519\" width=630 height=73 /></span><br><br>In Aeonica, there are many interesting potential partners.<br>Go on dates, deepen your relationships, and experience a romantic story that can lead to marriage and beyond.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/b39a70fc39d48f200c6af51712e3d697.poster.avif?t=1757359519\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/b39a70fc39d48f200c6af51712e3d697.webm?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/b39a70fc39d48f200c6af51712e3d697.mp4?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/c1386947550124f005b9759a34a7c886.avif?t=1757359519\" width=630 height=73 /></span><br><br>Whether it's fresh produce, handcrafted creations, or rare fish – decide what to sell and how your shop looks.<br>Take care of your spirit customers and make sure they keep coming back.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/d92257bbdbf0508ecb5ac515c20f694c.poster.avif?t=1757359519\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/d92257bbdbf0508ecb5ac515c20f694c.webm?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/d92257bbdbf0508ecb5ac515c20f694c.mp4?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/578aab66d6c31cb4e77757fabe87fe55.avif?t=1757359519\" width=630 height=73 /></span><br><br>Plant crops, raise animals, build pathways, and decorate your farm.<br>Create your own little paradise and supply your shop with fresh products.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/ff74d0b7dfad54265b2374f20af1633c.poster.avif?t=1757359519\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792780/extras/ff74d0b7dfad54265b2374f20af1633c.webm?t=1757359519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\">